	"keywords": "Information Security, Infosec, Cybersecurity",
	"description": "Getting your first job in information security (infosec, or cybersecurity) can\nbe tough. \n\nIt&#x27;s (still) a relatively new industry, and job roles and descriptions aren&#x27;t\nalways consistent. Plus, it can be hard to figure out where to get started, what\nskills you need, and how you can acquire them.\n\nWhat&#x27;s more, there are a lot of statistics that talk about how many jobs there\nare in cyber security. This makes it sound as though it should be very easy to\nget a job without any experience. \n\nThe issu",
