	"keywords": "Privacy, Cybersecurity, Information Security, Data",
	"description": "What&#x27;s the difference between data privacy and data security?\n\nData security is about protecting your data from unauthorized access (basically\nensuring that hackers can&#x27;t access your data).\n\nData privacy, on the other hand, is about giving you more granular control over\nhow (and by whom) your data is accessed, used, or shared. \n\nBoth are extremely important. \n\nWhy is Data Privacy Important?\nThere are a couple big reasons you should care about data privacy (in addition\nto data security). \n\nCyberc",
