	"description": "A botnet is a collection of internet connected devices (anything from PCs to IoT\ndevices) which are infected by the same malware. \n\nA hacker uses the malware the botnet is infected with to control it and launch\nbotnet attacks. The attacks are more effective when launched using hundreds, or\nthousands, or even hundreds of thousands of linked devices. \n\nWhat&#x27;s the point of building a botnet?\nBotnets can be used for a variety of attacks:\n\n * Generate fake advertising clicks to increase site revenue ",
